f time I went to 25. <BR>  <BR> Wotan</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#CCCCCC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/btheshanks.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=blye>Blye</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Administrator</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>1/12/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>4:59:49 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: New Recruits</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">We need some more input on this quickly.  We need to get the rules laid down and stick with them, as it prevents confusion as to what to do when a player asks to join our guild. </font><P>Leader of the Shanks, until I get killed or you find somebody better...<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#a8a8a8><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubluudthirsty.showPublicProfile>Bluud Thirsty</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Global user</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>1/12/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>5:41:41 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: New Recruits</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Sounds good to me.  <BR>  <BR> The only reason I would entertain the idea of letting more in is the fact I know we will be taking some heat for our ideology.  <BR>  <BR> I think we need to recruit strong now on the safehouse boards. Lets advertise. <BR>  <BR> Th